@title: POINTERS

@description: he pointer symbol (*) must be attached to the associated
 variable, with no spaces.

```c
int *a;                            /* OK */
int* a;                            /* C - V3 violation */
int*a;                             /* C - V3 violation */
int a = 3 * b;                     /* OK */
int strlen(char const *str);       /* OK */
```

This rule applies only in the pointer context.


